item.title: Robotics
item.dc:creator: Comrade_Tiki
item.description:
Oh yeahhh! I remember my amazement when I saw it withstand that kick-shove from the side. And as silly as it seemed on the ice, a horse would have broken a leg or three there.

That thing seriously needs a quieter motor, though. At the end with the tethered debris-crossing it became a ninja.
